THIS IS THE GAME OF LIFE; PLAYED ONA 5x5 FIELD. IN RESPONSE TO THEPROMPT; ENTER THE COORDINATES OFEACH LIVE STARTING CELL; FOLLOWED BYA ZERO. FOR EXAMPLE: 3;2;0WHEN YOU INPUT THE LAST CELL; ENTERONE INSTEAD OF ZERO FOR THE THIRDVALUE. FOR EXAMPLE: 4;4;1THE PROGRAM WILL THEN DISPLAY THESTARTING CONFIGURATION; FOLLOWED BYSUCCEEDING GENERATIONS.THE VARIABLE B CONTAINS THE SIZE OFTHE PLAYFIELD; SO YOU CAN CHANGE BTO ANY VALUE UP TO 9. PRESS <CTRL>-CTO STOP.